metadata.name: Spring of Gangland - by Eddie Gangland
metadata.description:
The “Seasons of Gangland” drop is an art-focused NFT drop to wrap up the year of 2022. Eddie Gangland has created 4 original scenes; one each for Summer, Winter, Spring and Fall to showcase the beautiful world of Gangland throughout the year. Watch the world of Gangland come to life as Gangboy takes you on an adventure that includes everything from surfing to building snowmen! 

Eddie Gangland is a street artist and NFT creator most recently recognized for his Gangboy character and the Gangland universe he is in the act of building. Eddie has been featured in publications like Vogue and RollingStone because of his artwork and metaverse builds. Eddie continues blending the real world and web 3 with his art as as he hits the streets putting up artwork while also minting nfts for his fast growing community.
